int alphabet_position_sum(String s, int k) {
    int sum = 0;
    for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
        sum += c - 'a' + 1;
    }
    for (int i = 0; i < k; i++) {
        int new_sum = 0;
        while (sum > 0) {
            new_sum += sum % 10;
            sum /= 10;
        }
        sum = new_sum;
    }
    return sum;
}
```

